Package org.voltdb

Main package for VoltDB contains public interfaces.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    VoltTable
    The primary representation of a result set (of tuples) or a temporary table in VoltDB.
    VoltTable.ColumnInfo
    Object that represents the name and schema for a VoltTable column.
    VoltTableRow
    Represents the interface to a row in a VoltTable result set.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    VoltType
    Represents a type in a VoltDB Stored Procedure or VoltTable.
